00:19:27.560 --> 00:19:32.200
as leaf-cutter ants
are agricultural.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:35.230
And so their crops
are only found

00:19:35.230 --> 00:19:37.540
with their particular nest.

00:19:37.540 --> 00:19:41.470
That nest has a relationship
with that particular breed

00:19:41.470 --> 00:19:44.890
of crop and will
kill anything that

00:19:44.890 --> 00:19:48.307
looks identical to us
that comes from outside.

